---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="From the Ashes — Michalina Sablik">
  <div class="container page-content">
    <h1>From the Ashes</h1>
    <p class="exhibition-detail-venue">Zachęta National Gallery of Art, Warsaw | 2024</p>
    <div class="exhibition-detail-body">
      <p>The exhibition presents young artists' responses to crises since 2020, framed through phoenix mythology narrative. All works were made after 2020 and are organized into two thematic sections.</p>
      <p>"Flame" addresses climate, economic, and social crises using digital aesthetics and new technologies. "Birth" presents speculative ecological-technological futures with utopian and solarpunk narratives. The exhibition features 17 participating artists.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="exhibition-detail-credits">
      <p><strong>Opens:</strong> March 15, 2024</p>
      <p><strong>Curator:</strong> Michalina Sablik</p>
    </div>
    <div class="exhibition-gallery" style="margin-top: 2.5rem; display: grid; gap: 1rem;">
      <img src="/images/exhibitions/from-the-ashes/1.jpg" alt="Exhibition view" loading="lazy" style="width:100%; border-radius: 4px;" />
      <img src="/images/exhibitions/from-the-ashes/2.jpg" alt="Exhibition view" loading="lazy" style="width:100%; border-radius: 4px;" />
